track_notes: No problem to park at the starting point, the place is wonderfull; on summit where no much people goes you will have lot of place for antenna; behave for you are in the central part of the Mercantour Park, not to pick up flowers or any thing else.
This track is shorter! you need a 4 wheels drive to reach the end of the forest road from St Dalmas.
This path is not very difficult, but you need to be in good health. The place is wonderfull, the panorama 360d all around, and if lucky you will see some mountain goat.
